io.parallec.core.config

Class ParallecGlobalConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.parallec.core.config.ParallecGlobalConfig

  • public class ParallecGlobalConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    this is the global system config. You can replace the values here before executing them. Different from those settings defined in ParallelTaskConfig, settings here are effective to all executions, and cannot be overwritten for a particular task.
    Author:
    Yuanteng (Jeff) Pei
